&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;2. अर्धरोगहरी निद्रा ।&lt;/em&gt;
Proper sleep cures half of the diseases..&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;3 मुद्गदाली गदव्याली ।&lt;/em&gt;
Of all the Pulses, Green grams are the best. It boosts Immunity. Other Pulses all have one or the other side effects.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
